TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Goodbye.
Charwood out in nowhere. Who keep it safe?
Text: 그을린숲 아무것도 없는 곳에 있어. 누가 안전 지켜?

TextEng: I'm hunting for a cult that promoted plague in Neverwinter.
Text: 저는 네버윈터에 역병을 퍼뜨린 사교를 추적하고 있습니다.

TextEng: Tell me about Charwood.
Have you heard of any trouble around here?
Me looks for plague-cult. They hurt Neverwinter.
Text: 나 역병 사교 찾아. 걔들 네버윈터 해쳤어.

TextEng: Tell stuff abouts Charwood.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
Charwood seems pretty isolated. Who protects you?
Text: 그을린숲은 꽤 외딴 것 같은데. 누가 당신들을 보호하나요?

TextEng: Do you have shops? Merchants?
You gots equipments?
I've spoken to you before. Don't you remember?
But you seen me before. You not remember?
Text: 전에 나 봤잖아. 기억 안 나?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> New? Port Llast is well established.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 새로 만들어졌다고요? 라스트 항구는 이미 잘 자리 잡았는데요.

TextEng: Where are your guards? Perhaps they know?
Text: 경비병들은 어디 있나요? 그들이 알지도 모르겠네요.

TextEng: You gots guards? Maybe they knows?
Who are the important people in town?
Who important around here?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are you afraid of that other Jhareg?
Who Quint?
Who is Quint?
I want to ask something else about Charwood.
Text: 그을린숲에 대해 다른 걸 물어보고 싶어요.

TextEng: Me ask something else about town.
Why don't you remember?
Why you not remember stuff?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> The Hall of Justice is a very old building.
Where can I find the Mayor?
Where me find Mister Mayor?
Do the Jharegs have a castle?
Them Jar-Eggs, they have castle?
What does the guard protect you from?
What da guard protect you from?
Me want know 'bout dem peoples.
Tell me about the different people around here.
Text: 이 근처 여러 사람들에 대해 말해주세요.
